{"tid":2052024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼致信聯合國指控中國對南海主張","createTime":"2020-06-05T08:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T17:42:45.000Z","uid":92376,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"82382153043807d47c17bd0bcde143cc40196e14","tid":2052024,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:05:35.000Z","msg":"內容節錄：<br />\n<br />\n長蕾特...國遞發<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/482263/印尼致信聯合國指控中國對南海主張\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F482263%2F%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E8%87%B4%E4%BF%A1%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%BB%E5%BC%B5&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=4b3991c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/482263/印尼致信聯合國指控中國對南海主張</a><br />\n<br />\n完整新聞請瀏覽超連結"},{"pid":"2f1e21abc91824f357ff54c92b984983976dd11d","tid":2052024,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍，不遠矣"},{"pid":"4f4cf2c50f963846fae1a4e37336df8079ad24ca","tid":2052024,"uid":56115,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:09:49.000Z","msg":"支那01就唔使咁做啦<br />\n<br />\n據《日本經濟新聞》6月4日報道，印尼外長蕾特諾（Retno Marsudi）6月4日在面向海外記者的新聞會上稱，已經向聯合國遞發信，抗議中國在南海主張有主權。<br />\n<br />\n這封日期為5月26日的信函明確反對中國劃定的「九段線」，以及在該海域內主張的歷史性主權。"},{"pid":"e6c6d60a2b29aa3f3fbc22606d0a4bc010979fa3","tid":2052024,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f1e21abc91824f357ff54c92b984983976dd11d","tid":2052024,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍，不遠矣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"八國咁少？"},{"pid":"b7df49977bde7ae59f9103f6a22fee3647abb326","tid":2052024,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"4f4cf2c50f963846fae1a4e37336df8079ad24ca","tid":2052024,"uid":56115,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:09:49.000Z","msg":"支那01就唔使咁做啦<br />\n<br />\n據《日本經濟新聞》6月4日報道，印尼外長蕾特諾（Retno Marsudi）6月4日在面向海外記者的新聞會上稱，已經向聯合國遞發信，抗議中國在南海主張有主權。<br />\n<br />\n這封日期為5月26日的信函明確反對中國劃定的「九段線」，以及在該海域內主張的歷史性主權。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"我嚴格遵守lihkg版規<br />\n不做任何侵犯新聞創作行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c5d9c21f753d0ad2fc69e9c37906390b82a7f8","tid":2052024,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"印尼致信聯合國指控中國對南海主張<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即時國際<br />\n撰文：陳蹊<br />\n2020-06-05 15:47<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-06-05 15:47<br />\n<br />\n印尼政府6月4日突然宣布，5月底時已經向聯合國（UN）控訴中國的南海主張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHTQZFr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHTQZFr.jpg&h=d1c88e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼一名負責海洋事務的官員指出印尼北部納土納群島的位置。2019年12月底，印尼指控中國漁政船多次保護捕魚船隻進入印尼專屬經濟海域。（Reuters）<br />\n<br />\n據《日本經濟新聞》6月4日報道，印尼外長蕾特諾（Retno Marsudi）6月4日在面向海外記者的新聞會上稱，已經向聯合國遞發信，抗議中國在南海主張有主權。<br />\n<br />\n這封日期為5月26日的信函明確反對中國劃定的「九段線」，以及在該海域內主張的歷史性主權。<br />\n<br />\n信函支持海牙國際法庭在2016年7月下達的認為「九段線」缺乏國際法依據的裁定。蕾特諾在新聞會上強調：「中國的主張可能對印尼專屬經濟海域造成影響，印尼政府堅持一貫立場。」<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，與菲律賓、越南以及馬來西亞不同，印尼在南海領土權問題上與中國並無直接爭議。但是，印尼的納土納群島位於南海南端，群島周邊的印尼專屬經濟海域與「九段線」重合。因此，印尼對中國漁船多次在該海域作業加強警惕。"},{"pid":"1cba7c900d011ed92200bf1f8531e4f43d689223","tid":2052024,"uid":227769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:41:15.000Z","msg":"全盛時期ge支國可以同時得罪幾多個國家？"},{"pid":"f8e3897487f23bc75e5d9f9ed88f610e38108d23","tid":2052024,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:43:32.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係風起了<br />\n印尼都過黎玩埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94172f660010873eb5e0187f924fbad342292698","tid":2052024,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4526fe8b05e953a7fcd0cd9a8d38eb622cf823","tid":2052024,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"印尼直接出兵啦"},{"pid":"647c7f1078b4a228d13d432862dc5f866ea9b93f","tid":2052024,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T11:14:41.000Z","msg":"好國襲擊狗國"},{"pid":"a6216aa759e0bbcc8c20b4e10d957dbeec827b77","tid":2052024,"uid":267647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"可能大家都忍左好耐<br />\n呢個moment終於要爆"},{"pid":"548ce21080467ca1d6a070781edf178fada329a5","tid":2052024,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"印尼由以前已經反共反華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔奇"},{"pid":"851bfdbaf2d92df9c2bc904c41613ad0cf4ebf04","tid":2052024,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T17:42:45.000Z","msg":"經濟要起飛了"}]}